      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014117&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3331&rangeEnd=3427",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5b0322e0813ab6c03g0176af?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3331&rangeEnd=3427"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014117_8_6039-6135",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6039-6135",
      "markText": "学习发展心理学的学生必须从各个学科或领域获取知识，包括心理学、精神病学、社会学、人类学、生物学、遗传学（研究遗传特征的学科）、家庭学（研究家庭关系的跨领域学科）、教育学、历史学、哲学和医学等。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014117&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6039&rangeEnd=6135",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5b0322e0813ab6c03g0176af?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6039&rangeEnd=6135"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014117_8_22095-22193",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "22095-22193",
      "markText": "同辈（cohort）是指同一年龄段的人组成的群体；而特定历史时代的人虽然包含同一年龄段的群体，但是并不是所有的同辈都属于这一群体，除非在他们生命的某个重要时期都经历了某些重大历史事件",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014117&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=22095&rangeEnd=22193",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5b0322e0813ab6c03g0176af?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=22095&rangeEnd=22193"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014117_8_3842-3901",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3842-3901",
      "markText": "狄特里克发现，婴儿更喜欢吮吸包裹甜食的布而不是护士的手指，于是他便推断吮吸这一动作“不是天生的本能，而是后天习得的”（",
      "totalCount": 117,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014117&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3842&rangeEnd=3901",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5b0322e0813ab6c03g0176af?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3842&rangeEnd=3901"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014117_8_3667-3727",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3667-3727",
      "markText": "发展心理学的科学研究先驱是婴儿传记，即某些记录儿童早期发展的日志。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014117&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3667&rangeEnd=3727",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5b0322e0813ab6c03g0176af?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3667&rangeEnd=3727"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014117_8_11273-11306",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "11273-11306",
      "markText": "青少年期的主要目标是寻求同一性——无论是人格的、性别的还是职业的。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014117&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11273&rangeEnd=11306",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5b0322e0813ab6c03g0176af?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=11273&rangeEnd=11306"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014117_8_24525-24612",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "24525-24612",
      "markText": "我思我秀？ 你能回想发生在你生活的时代改变了家庭及儿童生活的一件重大文化事件吗？你又将如何研究此事件所造成的影响？",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014117&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=24525&rangeEnd=24612",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5b0322e0813ab6c03g0176af?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=24525&rangeEnd=24612"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014117_8_9477-9535",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "9477-9535",
      "markText": "社会建构是指，在某一特定时期社会成员所普遍接受的对于某一事物本质的看法，也就是基于普遍认同的理解或假设而形成的观念。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014117&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9477&rangeEnd=9535",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5b0322e0813ab6c03g0176af?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9477&rangeEnd=9535"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014117_8_10364-10834",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "10364-10834",
      "markText": "我们将把生理发展和认知发展合并到一章进行讨论。 表1-1对个体各个时期的划分不够细致，也略显武断。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014117&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10364&rangeEnd=10834",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5b0322e0813ab6c03g0176af?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10364&rangeEnd=10834"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014117_8_27203-27249",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "27203-27249",
      "markText": "生命全程中的任何一个时期都会受到过去经历的影响，反过来，该时期的经历又会影响个体今后的发展。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014117&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=27203&rangeEnd=27249",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5b0322e0813ab6c03g0176af?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=27203&rangeEnd=27249"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300014117_8_31310-31388",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "31310-31388",
      "markText": "你有没有发现有关吉妮和维克特的研究中所存在的道德问题？如果研究是为了获得知识，从而导致参与研究的个体在研究过程中受到伤害，那么这种研究是否还值得我们去进行？",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300014117&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=31310&rangeEnd=31388",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5b0322e0813ab6c03g0176af?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=31310&rangeEnd=31388"
    },
    {
